---
description: MYLIT test, commit, push, deploy workflow
alwaysApply: true
---

Before shipping, run:

cd /workspace/lit-app
npx tsc --noEmit
npx expo export -p web

Then commit safe files only, push to main, and deploy production:

cd /workspace
git status
git add .
git reset -- .env .env.local .vercel lit-app/.env lit-app/.env.local lit-app/.vercel || true
git commit -m "Describe the MYLIT update clearly"
GIT_SSH_COMMAND="ssh -i ~/.ssh/id_ed25519_mylit -o IdentitiesOnly=yes" git push origin main

cd /workspace/lit-app
npx --yes vercel@latest --prod --yes

Do not ask Isaac to push or deploy unless authentication fails.
